t marketplace.  aDescription based on information from the publisher. 0aIntercultural communication. 0aCross-cultural orientation. 0aInternational relations and culture. 0aPerforming arts. 4aElectronic books.2 aMichigan Publishing (University of Michigan)epublisher. 0aTheater--text/theory/performance.40zAccess to the Michigan Publishing online version:uhttps://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.8765418